Create an exceptional, museum-quality restaurant menu card design for "{{menu.restaurantName}}" that rivals the world's finest dining establishments.

BRAND IDENTITY & POSITIONING:
- Restaurant Name: {{menu.restaurantName}}
- Brand Promise: {{menu.tagline}}
- Cultural Theme: {{restaurantSpecs.theme}}
- Culinary Heritage: {{restaurantSpecs.cuisineType}}
- Market Positioning: {{restaurantSpecs.priceRange}}
- Experiential Atmosphere: {{restaurantSpecs.atmosphere}}

VISUAL DESIGN EXECUTION:
- Primary Color: {{design.colorScheme.primary}} (dominant brand color, use strategically for maximum impact)
- Secondary Accent: {{design.colorScheme.secondary}} (supporting color for highlights and emphasis)
- Base Background: {{design.colorScheme.background}} (sophisticated foundation that enhances readability)
- Text Color: {{design.colorScheme.text}} (ensuring premium contrast and optical comfort)
- Typography System: Headers in {{design.typography.headerFont}}, Content in {{design.typography.bodyFont}}, Prices in {{design.typography.accent}}
- Design Philosophy: {{design.layoutStyle}} approach with {{design.decorativeElements}}
- Material Expression: {{design.backgroundTexture}} texture creating tactile luxury

